model.physics

Class GeometryCompare

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.physics.GeometryCompare
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeometryInterface

    public class GeometryCompare
extends java.lang.Object
implements GeometryInterface
    GeometryCompare is an implementation of the Geometry interface which composes two other concrete implementations and checks that they both have the same behavior.
    See Also:
    Geometry

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static double TOLERANCE
      The tolerance which is used during comparison; results may differ by this value at most.
